data.description: 100 % FINANCING AVAILABLE and ZERO DOWN PAYMENT AVAILABLE !Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in a quiet and welcoming neighborhood. With new fixtures and beautiful wood plank flooring, this home exudes a warm and inviting ambiance. The spacious kitchen boasts a huge pantry and ample counter space, for culinary enthusiasts. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living areas, for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones. Whether you're an investor seeking a promising opportunity or a first-time homebuyer, this property is a great choice. A convenient location, by the interstate and restaurants, as well as its proximity to the levee, offers a range of recreational activities and easy access to amenities. Don't miss the chance to make this lovely house your new home, where comfort, convenience, and a welcoming atmosphere await you.
